  <para style="li4" vid="NUM 7:65">That was everything that Abidan, the son of Gideoni, brought as his offering.<verse eid="NUM 7:65"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="66" style="v" sid="NUM 7:66"/>On the tenth day Ahiezer, the son of Ammishaddai, brought his offering. Ahiezer was the leader of the people of Dan.<verse eid="NUM 7:66"/></para>
